<div type="translation" source="bib:Gillet2024_01">

<p>Fortune! Prosperity! This is the 2nd year of Kōpparakesarivarman. <supplied reason="lost">To</supplied> Mahādeva <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>mahadeva &gt; mahādeva</foreign></supplied> of the shrine <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gṛhatu</foreign></supplied> of the Lord <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>īśvara</foreign></supplied> [of] Pakaiviṭai of Maṉṉupperumpaḻuvūr of Kuṉṟakkūṟṟam, the Paṭṭu<supplied reason="lost">ṭaiyārs</supplied> of the shrine <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gṛhattu</foreign></supplied> of the Lord <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>īśvara</foreign></supplied> [of] Avanikantaṟpa <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> </p></div>

